   </div>
  </div>. The reflectivities used correspond to fractionalities α = 0.28, 0.60, 1.00, and 1.72. Errors were estimated as a square root inverse of the number of measurements (Supplementary Materials). The second-order interferometric visibility reached values between 71.4 and 98.6% for 
